curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/11649' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM37603", "table_name": "PIN DESCRIPTION", "content": "PIN DESCRIPTION  PIN  NAME  I/O  FUNCTION  WLCSP-1.78×1.36-12B  TDFN-3×3-12L  A1  6  LED1  I  Current Sink 1. The boost converter regulates the minimum  voltage between current sinks to VHR.  A2  7  NC  —  No Connection.  A3  8  GND  O  Ground Pin.  B1  4  LED2  I  Current Sink 2. The boost converter regulates the minimum  voltage between current sinks to VHR.  B2  5  SDA  I/O  I2C Data Signal.  B3  9  SW  I  Drain Connection for Internal Low-side N-Channel MOSFET.  Connect to the anode of an external Schottky diode.  C1  2  LED3  I  Current Sink 3. The boost converter regulates the minimum  voltage between current sinks to VHR.  C2  3  SCL  I  I2C Clock Signal.  C3  10  OUT  I  Output Voltage Sense Pin. It is used for sensing the output  voltage for over-voltage protection. Connect to the positive  terminal of the output capacitor.  D1  1  PWM  I  PWM Dimming Signal Input.  D2  12  HWEN  I  Hardware Enable Input Pin. Drive HWEN high to enable the  device and allow I2C write commands or PWM control.  D3  11  IN  I  Input Supply Pin. Connect a at least 2.2μF bypass capacitor  from IN to GND.  —  Exposed Pad  AGND  —  Power Ground Exposed Pad. It should be connected to ground  plane.    NOTE: I: input; O: output; I/O: input or output.         SGM37603  High Efficiency 3-String White LED Driver      4  JANUARY 2019  SG Micro Corp  www.sg-micro.com  "}'
